y.geom
Class AffineLine

java.lang.Object
  y.geom.AffineLine

public class AffineLine
extends Object

This class represents a line in the 2D-dimensional affine space. The line is defined by the equation ax + by + c = 0

Constructor Summary

          Creates an affine line which is defined by two points.
